      "scen": "['Cause and effect are obvious to everyone and the right answer is self-evident.', 'Cause and effect are knowable but need expert analysis before the right answer is clear.', 'Cause and effect are only clear in hindsight, so the team must run safe-to-fail experiments.', 'There is no discernible cause and effect and a crisis is unfolding, so you must act immediately to establish order.']"
